      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772238498176,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "On 20th Feb started experimenting with \nLMStudio as it is becoming the backend for \nthe AI models loading and serving from \nLocal server. Their development speed is \nvery high.",
