      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "On 20th Feb started experimenting with \nLMStudio as it is becoming the backend for \nthe AI models loading and serving from \nLocal server. Their development speed is \nvery high.",
